author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Digital ID. The UK and many parts of the world are considering using digital identification and while it's definitely convenient, I'm cautious looking at the current governments of the world and trusting them with the ability to surveil us even more granularly than before. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: You Need To Fight Back Against Digital ID...
